pages.title: Home
pages.description: CityPackz is a collectibles business that specializes in selling game cards and Hot Wheels. We offer a wide selection of game cards from popular trading card games, as well as a variety of Hot Wheels cars and track sets. Whether you're a collector or just looking for the perfect gift, CityPackz has something for everyone. Explore our collection and start building your own unique collection today!

pages.title: About Us
pages.description: At CityPackz, our mission is to provide a platform for local businesses to connect with customers and grow. We are passionate about supporting the community and fostering engagement between businesses and customers. Our goal is to offer high-quality products and services that help businesses stand out and attract customers. With CityPackz, businesses can discover new opportunities and build meaningful relationships within the ecosystem. Join us in creating a thriving community of local businesses and customers!
